    public class Avatar
extends java.awt.Rectangle
    An Avatar is a Rectangle that will move based on their user's keyboard entry.

      • avatarChoices

        public java.awt.Image avatarChoices(int index)
        Adds all possible Avatar images into an ArrayList (declared class above) so the user may choose and set an index.

        VARIABLE DICTIONARY:
        aChoices An ArrayList of Images that will store the possible Avatars. The user will pick one out of this list in Settings if they choose.

        Parameters:
        index - The index of which Avatar will be used. It is set by the user.
        Returns:
        Image The Image that the user wants to be their Avatar.
